Korean Street Cup Chicken
Serves 3

Ingredients

For Marinate Chicken 
1 1/2 chicken thighs, cut into bite size
1/2 tsp salt
1/2 tsp black pepper
1 Tbs rice wine
2 cloves garlic, grated
1/2 tsp ginger, grated

Frying oil
1/3 cup tempura powder
3 Tbs cold water
6 oz Korean rice cake, cut into bite size

For Sauce
2 tsp gochugan, Korean red pepper paste
1 tsp soy sauce
1 1/2 Tbs strawberry jam (you can substitute with any fruit jam/jelly)
2 Tbs ketchup
1 1/2 Tbs worcestershire sauce   http://amzn.to/2kvxoga
2 Tbs sugar
1/4 cup water
2 cloves garlic, chopped

For Garnish
1 Tbs sesame seeds
